text: Lakovic or Lakovič (Serbian Cyrillic: Лаковић) is a gender-neutral Slavic surname that may refer to *Elvir Laković Laka (born 1969), Bosnian rock singer-songwriter *Jaka Lakovič (born 1978), Slovenian basketball player and coach *Predrag Laković (1929–1997), Serbian actor *Sasha Lakovic (1971–2017), Canadian ice hockey player
title: Lakovic
